data.description: In an active 55+ community this is a spacious unit in excellent condition with an amazing view. Features newer washer/dryer, newer water heater, granite counters tops, impact windows and a beautiful water view from screening in balcony. Only one owner, very clean and well maintained the unit is ready to move in. Located near all major shopping, Seminole casino, hospital and restaurants. Also, close to the Turnpike and Sawgrass Expressway. The community offers billiards, 3 heated pools, shuffleboard, walk/jogging path and clubhouse with activities. Low maintenance includes cable TV, water, trash, insurance and common ground maintenance.
